Notes:
A/N	Alphanumeric
APA	All Points Addressable
	(alphanumeric display is not presently supported)

C	Adapter type = CGA
E	Adapter type = EGA
M	Adapter type = Mono adapter
H	Adapter type = Hercules (not BIOS compatible)

Mx	Same mode with ega having more than 64k memory.
Ex	Same mode when an Enhanced Color Display is attached.

Num Colors = 4M refers to different mono attributes:
Color	Attribute
0x0	Black
0x3	White
0xC	Blinking
0xF	Intensified

